WEBVTT

00:01:27.560 --> 00:01:32.440
The one thing that struck me was that 
our nation is such a young democracy,

00:01:32.440 --> 00:01:36.200
and here is such an old lady
going to cast her vote.

00:01:36.200 --> 00:01:37.840
There were print and 
television journalists 


00:01:37.840 --> 00:01:40.840
and photographers there.

00:01:40.840 --> 00:01:44.120
I also took her name and address 
before leaving.

00:01:44.120 --> 00:01:45.640
Some months later,

00:01:45.640 --> 00:01:49.880
I went to her village looking for her.

